  <para style="toc3">Amus</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ka baseen ni Amus</para>
  <para style="mt1">Amus</para>
  <para style="is">Igpewun-a</para>
  <para style="ip">Si Amus ka hun-a ne prupita diye te Bibliya ne hapit egkaamin-amin ka nasulat. Minsan ke migpuun sikandin te lungsud te Huda, piru migwali sikandin diye te igkahibang ne balabahan dapit te igsile ne migharian ne iyan ka Israil, te elat-elat te igkawalu ne pulu ne leg-un te ware pad neetew si Kristu. (me 750 te ware pad neetew si Hisus) Te seeye ne timpu migmatubung wey migtuman te balaud te simbaan ka me etew wey ware igkabantali ran. Piru nakita ni Amus ne iyan de migmatubung ka me meyaman tenged te pegdeeg-deeg dan te ware egkengeyimu wey ware matareng ne peggukum kandan. Ware migpuun te pusung dan ka pegtuman te keet-etawan te me balaud te intuuwan dan wey ware keupianan ka ware igkabantali ran. Migwali si Amus te ware pegkaaldek ne eglegparan te Magbebaye ne Manama ka nasud. Migbagget sikandin ne igpalepew ka matareng ne peggukum diye te hukumanan ke ma ke egkeyid-u red ka Magbebaye ne Manama te nenasame ne me etew te seini ne nasud.” (5:15)</para>
  <para style="iot">Ka nenasulat te seini ne baseen</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka peggukum te me nasud ne sumbaley te Israil 1:1-2:5</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka peggukum te Israil 2:6-6:14</para>
  <para style="io1">Ka lalimma ne immakita 7:1-9:15</para>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" />
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1: a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 15:1-7; 2Kru 26:1-23; </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">2Kru 14:23-29.</char>
    </note> Seini ka inlalag ni Amus, sabeka ne talagbantey te karniru te lungsud te Tikuwa. Impanengneng kandin seini te Magbebaye ne Manama te daruwa ne leg-un ka miglihad te ware pad miglilinug. Te seeye ne timpu iyan mighari si Usiyas te Huda ne si Hirubuwam ne anak ni Huwas ka mighari te Israil. NEW Seini ka ingkahi ni Amus ne sabeka ne talagtameng te me karniru te lungsud te Tikuwa. Impataha kandin te Magbebaye ne Manama ka seini ne lalag meyitenged te Israil te me daruwa ne leg-un te ware pad ka linug. Te timpu ne iyan Hari si Usiyas te Huda wey si Hirubuwam ne anak ni Huwas iyan Hari te Israil.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Huwil 3:16.</char>
    </note> Migkahi sikandin,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Impasegku-segku te Magbebaye ne Manama ka laheng din puun te Siyun,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impabawes din seini puun te Hirusalim. Ne nenaggangu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Miglungku. </char></note> ka me panabtaban,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ka me hilamunen diye te Bubungan te Karmil.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te Manama te me nasud ne marani te Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3-5: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 17:1-3; Hir 49:23-27; Sak 9:1.</char>
    </note> Ne seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka me matig-Damasku, sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan. Imbaybayaran dan amana ka nangugpe te Gilyad.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Inlupet dan sikandan te putew ne diekanan.</char></note> Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. <verse number="4" style="v" />Sikan naa, egpeuyanan ku te hapuy ka palasyu ni Hasail, ne eg-et-et te malig-en, matikang wey makepal ne alad ni Binhadad. NEW Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka palasyu ni Hari Hasail wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, makepal, wey matikang ne alad ni Hari Binadad. Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. <verse number="5" style="v" />Egguhusen ku ka pagul te gumawan te Damasku wey egdereetan ku ka Hari<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Talewusey.</char></note> te Bangalug te Abin, wey ka pangulu te Bangalug te Bit-abin. Ne ka nangugpe te Sirya<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Aram.</char></note> egkaddakep diye te Kir.” Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. NEW Egguhusen ku ka pagul te gumawan te Damasku wey egdereetan ku ka mahinged te napu te Abin, wey ka pangulu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Miggengen te tuked.</char></note>te Bit-idin. Ne ka nangugpe te Sirya egpandakepen wey egpanguyanen diye te Kir.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peggukum te Pilistiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:6-8: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 14:29-31; Hir 47:1-7; Isi 25:15-17; Huwil 3:4-8; Sup 2:4-7; Sak 9:5-7.</char>
    </note> Ne seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka me matig-Gasa. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan, su impandakep dan ka keet-etawan wey imbelegye dan diye te matig-Idum. <verse number="7" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka alad te Gasa wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, makepal, wey matikang ne alad kayi. <verse number="8" style="v" />Egdereetan ku ka Hari te Asdud, wey ka pangulu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: miggen-gen te tuked. </char></note> te Askalun. Eglegparan ku ka Ikrun wey egkengammatey degma ka nenasame ne Pilistihanun.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peggukum te Tiru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:9-10; </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 23:1-18; Isi 26:1—28:19; Huwil 3:4-8; Sak 9:1-4; Mat 11:21-22; Luk 10:13-14.</char>
    </note> Seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka me matig-Tiru. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan su ware dan tumana ka kasabutan dan ne egpeupianey se tagtahasuled, su impandakep dan ka keet-etewan wey imbelegye diye te matig-Idum. <verse number="10" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka alad te Tiru, wey egtutungen ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad kayi.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peggukun te Idumiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11-12; </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 34:5-17; 63:1-6; Hir 49:7-22; Isi 25:12-14; 35:1-15; Abd 1-14; Mal 1:2-5.</char>
    </note> Seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka me matig-Idum. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan tenged te impanlupug dan ka me suled dan ne matig-Israil wey impangimatayan dan te ware pegkeyid-u. Migpabulus-bulusan dan te egtulis sikandan tenged te mangunekune ne langet dan wey kene egkataman ka langet dan. <verse number="12" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka Timan, wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad te Busra.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peggukum te Amun</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:13-15: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Hir 49:1-6; Isi 21:28-32; 25:1-7; Sup 2:8-11.</char>
    </note> Ne seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka me matig-Amun. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku sikandan su egkaalamlam sikandan te tane, ne eyew egmaluag de iya ka tane dan, impangebuan dan minsan ka egkengaberes ne me malitan diye te Gilyad. <verse number="14" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka alad te Raba, wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad kayi. Egpanguleyi sikandan te timpu te pegpabunbunuey, wey egbebalisusu ka egmabunbunuey iling te makeseg ne baggiyu. <verse number="15" style="v" />Ne egkengeuripen ka Hari, wey ka me pangulu ran.” Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te Muwab</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1-3: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 15:1—16:14; 25:10-12; Hir 48:1-47; Isi 25:8-11; Sup 2:8-11.</char>
    </note> Ne seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu, wey hep-at. </char></note> egpakasale ka keet-etawan te Muwab. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan tenged su intutung dan ka tul-an te Hari te Idum taman te neigmuk. <verse number="2" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka Muwab wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad te Kiriyut. Ne egkengammatey ka me mahinged te Muwab te mangune-kune ne pegpabunbunuey, wey nalingutan te pegpanguleyi wey te pegparahing te me trumpita. <verse number="3" style="v" />Eggimatayan ku ka Hari<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Talewusey.</char></note> te Muwab wey iglagkes ku ka langun ne pangulu te sika ne inged,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te Manama te Huda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at. </char></note> egpakasale ka keet-etawan te Huda. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan su ware dan ikula ka me balaud ku wey ware dan tumana ka me suhu ku. Nalimbungan sikandan te me diyus-diyus ne impamakey dengan te me kaap-apuan dan. <verse number="5" style="v" />Sikan naa, egsilaban ku ka Huda wey egtutungen ku ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad te Hirusalim.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te Manama te Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Ne seini ka inlalag te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Layun <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Tatelu wey hep-at.</char></note> egpakasale ka keet-etawan te Israil. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku iya sikandan. Su imbelegye dan ka matareng para te pelata, wey ka ware egkeyimu, para te senge sukub ne sandal. <verse number="7" style="v" />Inleig-leig<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Impandiekan ka me ulu.</char></note> dan ka egkengaayu-ayu wey impangeyis dan ka ware egkengeyimu. Ne migpasaamuley ka amey wey anak te sabeka re ne malitan, wey te sika ne paahi ne nalinditan ka matulus ne ngaran ku. <verse number="8" style="v" />Nekeempet sikandan ka nangibat te timplu ran ne nambebelat te me manggad ne insaad te nenekeutang kandan. Nangiinum sikandan te binu diye te timplu te diyus-diyus dan, ne impanguwa ran puun te nenekeutang kandan.</para>
  <para style="p">NEW Nangibat sikandan diye te kakiliran te me altar ne nambebelat te manggad ne impangahew ran isip gerentiya. Nangiinum sikandan te binu diye te baley te diyus-diyus dan, ne impanguwa ran puun te nenekeutang kandan.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:9: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Diy 3:8-11.</char>
    </note> “Neyimu ran seini minsan migdereetan ku ka me Amurihanun ne egpekeiling kalayat te kayu ne sidar wey iling kakehal te kayu ne tugas. In-im-imuan ku sikandan dereeti iling te kayu ne warad sugpang wey warad tued. <verse number="10" style="v" />Impalihawang ku sikaniyu puun te Ihiptu wey indumaan diye te inged ne ware mahinged seled te hep-at ne pulu (40) ne leg-un. Innimu ku sika eyew egkaangey niyu ka tane te me Amurihanen. <verse number="11" style="v" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11: </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Num 6:1-8.</char></note> Eggimuwen ku ne prupita ka duma ne me anak niyu ne me lukes wey ka duma ne me kanakan ne egkeyimu ne Nasariyu. <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Ka Nasariyu iyan ka etew ne migpanaad diye te Manama ne kene eg-inum te binu, kene egpaalut wey kene eggen-gen te minatey.</char></note> Me matig-Israil, kene naa na malehet seini? Sikeddi ka Magbebaye ne Manama iyan miglalag kayi. <verse number="12" style="v" />Piru impeinum niyu te binu ka me Nasariyu wey ware niyu pepangguhura ka me prupita te igpalalag ku kandan. <verse number="13" style="v" />Ne kuntee, eglegparan ku sikaniyu, iling te kerumata ne kenad egpekeyipanew te mabehat ne dulan. NEW Purisu egdereetan ku sikaniyu due te inged niyu iling te kerumata ne kenad egpekeyipanew tenged te bebehati ne dulan. <verse number="14" style="v" />Kene egpakaalihu ka meiyal ne egpallahuy wey egkaawaan te keseg ka me mannekal, wey ka me bahani kene egpakaluwas minsan te kandan ne pegkeetew. <verse number="15" style="v" />Egpakapallahuy ka mangngateu ne eggamit te pane, wey ka me meiyal ne egpallahuy kene egpakapallahuy wey ka nanguntud te kudde kene egpakaalihu. NEW Egpallahuy ka mangngateu ne eggamit te pane, wey kenad egpakapallahuy ka me meiyal ne egpallahuy. <verse number="16" style="v" />Ne minsan ka mabulut amana ne sundalu egpallahuy ne ware kukumbaleen te sika ne aldew,” Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. NEW Ne minsan ka me bahani, egpallahuy ne kenad egpakakukumbale te seeye hangkuwa ne aldew.” Sika ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" />
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Pammineha niyu, keet-etawan te Israil, ka iglalag te Magbebaye ne Manama kaniyu te impalihawang din puun te Ihiptu. <verse number="2" style="v" />“Sikaniyu re te intiru ne kalibutan ka impili ku wey inggeyinawaan ku. Sikan naa eglegparan ku sikaniyu tenged te langun ne sale niyu.” NEW “Sikaniyu re te intiru ne kalibutan ka in-alam ku. Sikan naa, eglegparan ku sikaniyu tenged te langun ne sale niyu.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka himu te prupita</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Egparumeey naa ka daruwa ne etew</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ware sikandan nekeg-uyun?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Egginihel naa ka liyun diye te puwalas,</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ware egdawiyen din?</para>
  <para style="q1">Egngangang naa ka anak te liyun diye te ugpaan din ne sulung</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ware napammued din?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Egsahad naa ka bayaku te bitaya</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ware peen kayi?</para>
  <para style="q1">Egkabekas naa ka bitaya</para>
  <para style="q2">ke ware egsahad kayi?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Kene naa egkangilam ka me etew ke egparahingen ka trumpita? Ke due egginguma ne kareetan te sabeka ne siyudad, kene naa ne diye egpuun seini te Magbebaye ne Manama?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Kene iya eggimu ka Magbebaye ne Manama te minsan nekey</para>
  <para style="q2">ke kene din pad igpataha ka puhawang din diye te me suluhuanen din ne me prupita.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Hentew naa ka kene egkaaldek</para>
  <para style="q2">te pegginihel e te liyun?</para>
  <para style="q1">Te peglalag e te Magbebaye ne Manama; hentew naa ka kene egpakapangguhud te lalag din?</para>
  <para style="s">Ka peglegpad te Samariya</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Pangguhuri niyu ka nangugpe diye te malig-en, matikang wey makepal ne alad te Asdud wey Ihiptu. “Libulung kew diye te bubungan te Samariya wey pitawa niyu ka dakel ne kahubut wey ka pegpangimatey diye te siyudad.”</para>
  <para style="p">NEW Pangguhuri niyu ka nangugpe diye te me palasyu te Asdud wey Ihiptu ne egpalibulungen diye te bubungan te Samariya eyew egkapantew ran ka siyudad wey egkakita ran ka dakel ne gubut, wey ka pegleig-leig te me mahinged.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Piggipenu te seini ne me etew ka me baley ran te me kasangkapan pinaahi te pegpangimatey wey te pegpanakew. Ware nakataha sikandan ke egmenuwen te eg-uyag-uyag ne matareng. NEW Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Kene sikandan egkateu ne eggimu te meupiya. Innipenu dan ka me baley ran te me karatuan ne nakuwa ran pinaahi te pegpangimatey wey te pegpanakew. <verse number="11" style="v" />Purisu eglingutan te me kuntere ka tane dan, egguhusen ka me palasyu ran wey egdereetan ka me malig-en ne inged dan.” /NEW Purisu eglingutan te me kuntere ka tane dan wey egguhusen ka malig-en, matikang wey makepal ne alad dan wey egpangahawen ka malig-en, wey me matikang ne baley ran/palasyu ran.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Seini ka inlalag te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Iling ne ka sabeka ne talagbantey egsalukagmit puun te bebe te liyun te daruwa ne paa, wey ke limang naa ne talinga. Te iling kayi egpangabangan ka me anak te Israil ne migmanandigsandig te Samariya diye te pikungan te hibatanan, wey dibabew te ulunan ne sida te sabeka ne hibatanan. NEW Seini ka inlalag te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Su ke nekey ka egkeula-ula te sabeka ne talagtameng ne iyan naan de egkasalukagmit ka daruwa ne paa wey ke talinga naa te karniru ne indawi te liyun, iling naan ded degma kayi ka egtamanan te me kabuhalan ni Israil ne nangugpe diye te Samariya. Su pila-pila re kandan ka egkaluwas ne miggibat-hibat te me mateles ne hibatanan. <verse number="13" style="v" />Ay-ayari niyu te egpammineg seini wey panpanayi niyu degma ka me kabuhalan ni Hakub,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Manama. <verse number="14" style="v" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:14: </char><char style="xt" closed="false">2Har 23:15.</char></note> “Te aldew ne egparusaan ku ka keet-etawan te Israil tenged te me sale dan, egdereetan ku ka altar te Bitil. Egkahuhus ka me sungey te altar wey egkengeulug diye te tane. <verse number="15" style="v" />Egdereetan ku ka me baley ne para te maagsil ne timpu wey ka me baley para te meinit ne timpu. Ne egkalundus ka baley ne indayan-dayanan te me ngipen te ilipanti, wey egkagguhus ka derakel<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Masalig.</char></note> ne baley.”</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" />
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Pammineg kew kayi me malitan te Samariya. Nekeiling kew te me baka te Basan ne naay-ayaran te egpakeen, wey inlupihan niyu ka ware egkengeyimu, wey inleig-leing niyu ka egkaayu-ayu, wey imbanasalan niyu ka me asawa niyu ne eg-uyanan kew te egkeinum niyu!” <verse number="2" style="v" />Ne migsaad ka matulus ne Magbebaye ne Manama. “Egginguma ka timpu ne egpandakepen kew pinaahi te bunuwit. Ka tagse sabeka kaniyu egpekeiling te isda ne nabunuwit. NEW Ne migsaad ka Magbebaye ne Manama pinaahi te pegkamatulus din “Egginguma iya ka timpu ne egpandakepen kew pinaahi te bunuwit ne ka tagse sabeka kaniyu egpekeiling te nabunuwit ne isda. ALT Iling ne ka Magbebaye ne Manama matulus, migsaad sikandin, “Egginguma ka me timpu ne egpangganuyen kew nikandan pinaahi te me bunuwit, ne ka tagse sabeka kaniyu egpekeiling e te isda ne nabunuwit. <verse number="3" style="v" />Egpangganuyen kew diye te marani te naggebe ne alad wey igmandegpak kew diye te Harmun.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka pegsupak te me matig-Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Sikaniyu se me matig-Israil pangendiye kew te Bitil wey himu kew te sale diye. Pangendiye kew man-e te Gilgal wey timuli niyu ka sale niyu diye. Uyan kew te igmanubad niyu tagse maselem wey uyan kew te igkasapulu tagse igkatatelu ne aldew. <verse number="5" style="v" />Halad kew te paan ne due patulin eyew te pegpasalamat keddi, wey ipeggasal niyu ka in-uney-uney niyu te egdasag, su sikan ma iya ka igkeup-upii niyu ne eggimuwen!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />“Impabitil ku<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Malinis ne ngipen.</char></note> ka langun ne siyudad niyu wey egkabitil ka minsan hendei, piru ware kew red iya man-e miglibed kayi te keddi. <verse number="7" style="v" />Ware ku man-e ipalugsu ka uran minsan ingkeilangan niyu perem para te me pinamula niyu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Te tatelu ne bulan te kene pad ka peggani.</char></note> Impeuranan ku ka duma ne siyudad piru ware mule diye te duma. Impeuranan ku ka duma ne kamet, piru migmammara mule ka duma. <verse number="8" style="v" />Migmagguye e te pegkamareyi, ka keet-etawan te masulug ne siyudad, ne migpamitew te weyig te sumbaley ne siyudad piru ware egkeinum dan. Piru ware kew miglibed kayi te keddi. Kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="p">NEW Purisu nangendiye te duma ne lungsud ka mahinged te daruwa ne lungsud wey ke tatelu naa, eyew egpammitew te weyig, piru ware nakita ran ne eleg ne egkeinum dan. Minsan pad due, ware kew miglibed keddi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />“Impakalamahan ku te meinit wey impareralu ka me pinamula niyu. Impangeen te me talangas ka me pinamula niyu, ka me parasan, ka me igira wey ka me ulibu niyu. Piru ware kew iya man-e miglibed kayi te keddi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />“Impeuyanan ku sikaniyu te me dilus iling te inggimu ku diye te Ihiptu. Innimatayan ku ka me kanakan niyu te bunuanan<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Kampilan.</char></note> wey in-ahew ku ka me kudde niyu. Ne impasalerep ku sikaniyu te ngareg te nenammatey diye te me kampu niyu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Impaseled ku diye te lungag te irung niyu ka ngareg te kampu niyu.</char></note> Piru ware kew iya man-e miglibed kayi te keddi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:11: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Hin 19:24.</char>
    </note> “Indereetan ku ka duma kaniyu iling te pegdereet ku te Suduma wey Gumura. Egpekeiling kew te kayu ne nalegleg ne in-awe diye te hapuy. Piru ware kew iya man-e miglibed kayi te keddi,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. <verse number="12" style="v" />“Sikan naa, eggimuwen ku iya sika kaniyu, e keet-etawan te Israil. Ne puun su eggimuwen ku iya sika, pangandam kew te pegtemu te Manama niyu.”</para>
  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Ne migkahi si Amus, “Ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka miggimu te bubungan wey te kalamag.</para>
  <para style="q2">Impanengneng din te me etew ka suman-suman din.</para>
  <para style="q1">Innimu rin ka marusilem</para>
  <para style="q2">ne maaldew.</para>
  <para style="q1">Ne miggiphipanew sikandin diye te iddus te me labuntud. NEW Su ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka miggimu te bubungan wey te kalamag. Impanengneng din ka puhawang din te me etew. Imparusilem din ka egkaliwaswas pad wey miggiphipanew diye te iddus te me labuntud. Iyan din ngaran ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ne Amana ne Maresen ne Manama.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka pegbanasal te peg-inniyug te sale</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Pammineg kew keet-etawan te Israil! Eg-ulahingan ku sikaniyu te peglungku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" />Nareetan e ka mateles<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Telek.</char></note> ne Israil,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey kenad e egpakasasindeg.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nakabahed<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: eg-engkeran.</char></note> e sikandin diye te tane din</para>
  <para style="q2">wey ware minsan hentew ne egpekeenew kandin.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Ka sabeka ne libu (1000) ne me sundalu puun te siyudad, sabeka ne gatus (100) naan de ka egpekeuli. Ne migpeuyan te sabeka ne gatus (100) ka sabeka ne siyudad ne sapulu (10) naan de ka nasame, te baley te Israil.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Migkahi e man e ka Magbebaye ne Manama te keet-etawan te Israil, “Parani kew<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Pamitawa a.</char></note> keddi wey egkeuyag kew. <verse number="5" style="v" />Kene kew hendiye te Bitil. Kena a gerami nikaniyu te egpamitew diye te Bitil su egkeyimu seini ne ware kapabulusan. Kene kew man-e hendiye te Gilgal wey diye te Birsiba, su egkeuripen de degma sikandan.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Parani kew keddi me kabuhalan ni Husi, eyew egkeuyag kew. Su ke kene, eglusuran ku sikaniyu ne iling te hapuy ne egtutung te keet-etawan te Israil. Egkareetan ka Bitil wey ware egpakabalabag kayi. NEW “Pamitawa niyu ka Magbebaye ne Manama wey egkeuyag kew. Su emun ke kene kew, egpamaneug sikandin ne egpekeiling te hapuy wey egdulihisen din ka me kabuhalan ni Husi, wey egsilaban din ka Bitil ne warad iya egpekeebuk te hapuy. <verse number="7" style="v" />Mekeyid-u-hid-u kew se ware mig-ikul te matareng ne peggukum, wey migdiek-diek te katenged te me etew.”</para>
  <para style="p">NEW Mekeyid-u-hid-u kew ka innimu te meupiya ne peggukum diye te pepeiti ne delemetan wey imbalahad niyu ka katareng diye te tane.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne migkahi si Amus, “Ka Magbebaye ne Manama ka miggimu te me bituen,</para>
  <para style="q2">ne egngaranan te Panderawa wey Balatik.</para>
  <para style="q1">Inggimu rin ka delem ne malayag</para>
  <para style="q2">wey inggimu rin ka maaldew ne egpaddusilem.</para>
  <para style="q1">Sikandin ka miglibulung te weyig puun te dahat peendiye te gapun.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne impeuran din ded seini diye te tane. Magbebaye ne Manama ka ngaran din.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Talagdereet din te me mannekal ne me etew wey te malig-en, makepal wey matikang ne me alad dan.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />“Egdumutan niyu ka me etew ne mapahetpet ne egpatuman te eleg ne peggukum diye te hukumanan <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Gumawan te siyudad.</char></note> wey eg-ehetan niyu ka eglalag te kamalehetan. <verse number="11" style="v" />Tenged su indeeg-deeg niyu ka egkenga-ayu-ayu wey impanakawan niyu sikandan te me inggaani ran. Sikan naa, kene kew egpekeugpe te me baley ne inggimu puun te impanapsapan ne me batu wey egpamula kew te me paras, wey kene kew egpekeinum te binu puun te me pinamula niyu ne paras. <verse number="12" style="v" />Nakanengneng a ke mamenu karakel ka sale niyu wey makariyab-diyab ka neyimu niyu ne pegsupak. Imbaybayaran niyu ka me matareng, pinaahi te pegdawat niyu te suul, wey ware niyu himuwa ka matareng ne peggukum diye te ware egkekeyimu diye te libulungan. NEW Nakanengneng a ke mamenu karakel wey kabehat ka sale niyu. Imbaybayaran niyu ka me matareng, impamuyuan niyu te suul, wey ware niyu ay-ayari te eggusey ka egkengaayu-ayu diye te hukumanan. <verse number="13" style="v" />Iyan egdapit ka mareet te seini ne timpu. Sikan naa, ke matagseb ka, peeneng-eneng ke naan de.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />“Liberi niyu ka meupiya ne himu wey kene ne ka mareet eyew egkeuyag kew, wey puun due, egdumaan kew te Amana ne Maresen ne Magbebaye ne Manama, sumale te ingkahi niyu. NEW Himuwa niyu ka meupiya, kene ka mareet. Ne egdumaan kew te Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Maresen ne Manama, sumale te ingkahi niyu. <verse number="15" style="v" />Pakaddiyu kew te mareet wey iyan niyu awesa ka meupiya, wey ikula niyu ka matareng ne peggukum diye te hukumanan.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Gumawan te siyudad, kayi egkewusey ka apulanan su kayi ma egmatemtemuwey ka me igbuyag te lungsud.</char></note> Su kema ke egkeyid-u red ka Magbebaye ne Manama te nahaat ne me kabuhalan ni Husi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" />Sikan naa, migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Magbebaye ne Manama, “Egkarineg ka pegpanagyawan wey pegsinehew diye te me deralanen te siyudad. Egpangumawen ka me etew puun te me kamet dan eyew te pegdamag te me minatey duma te seeye se insuulan, eyew te peglungku. NEW Sikan naa, migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Manama, “Due pegpalumbibigtew wey pegsinehew diye te me deralanen te siyudad. Minsan ka diye te me kamet, egpangumawen sikandan eyew egdamag te me minatey duma te seeye se insuulan ne egsinehew. <verse number="17" style="v" />Egpandalawit ka me etew degma diye te me pinamulaan te paras su egliharan ku sikaniyu langun eyew te peglegpad kaniyu.” Seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" />Ne migkahi e man-e si Amus, “Amana ne makaalat-halat se egkeyitabu kaniyu te migtetahad te aldew te Magbebaye ne Manama. Mania te egkeupian kew te aldew te Magbebaye ne Manama? Aldew kangkuwa seeye te karusileman wey kene ne malayag. <verse number="19" style="v" />Egpekeiling kew te sabeka ne etew ne migpallahuy te liyun ne nasi naampad iya nakasig-ung te usu, wey ke nakaseled e sikandin te baley, piru te peggen-gen din te alabat, ingkahat e nasi te uled. <verse number="20" style="v" />Amana ne durusilemi wey kene ne malayag ka aldew te Magbebaye ne Manama. Ware keupinanan te sika ne aldew wey amana ne durusilemi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:21-22: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Isa 1:11-14.</char>
    </note> Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Nalangetan a te me sahakeen niyu wey wara ad iya nahale te me matulus ne kalibulunganan niyu. <verse number="22" style="v" />Minsan pad eg-uyanan a nikaniyu te egtutungen ne igpanubad, wey te me halad ne trigu, kene ku egdawaten sika. Ne kene ku degma egsagmanen ka eg-uyanen niyu kayi te keddi ne impalambeg ne mananap. <verse number="23" style="v" />Peen-enenga niyu ka mahulub ne me ulahingen niyu. Kena a egkeupian ne egpammineg te me alpa niyu. <verse number="24" style="v" />Piru, ipakita niyu ka matareng ne peggukum iling te weyig ne egdalanag wey ka katareng ne iling te beuhan ne kene egkeetiyan.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:25-27: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Him 7:42-43.</char>
    </note> “Te diye pad te inged ne mammara ka me kaap-apuan niyu seled te (40) hep-at ne pulu ne leg-un, mighalad naa sikandan kayi te keddi? Ware! NEW “Keet-etawan te Israil, migpanubad kew naa wey mighalad keddi diye te inged ne kene egkeugpaan seled te te hep-at ne pulu (40) ne leg-un? <verse number="26" style="v" />Na, tianga niyud ka nangimu niyu ne me larawan te me diyus-diyus ne si Sakut, ka Hari niyu, wey si Kaiwan, ka diyus-diyus niyu ne bituen! <verse number="27" style="v" />Ne tenged due, igpeuripen ku sikaniyu diye te inged ne kewun-aan pad te Damasku,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Manama.</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka karereetan te Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ne migkahi si Amus, “Amana ne makaalat-halat ka egkeyitabu kaniyu te me pangulu te Siyun wey kaniyu te me pangulu te Samariya ne mig-ugpe ne matubung wey ware igkabantali, sikaniyu se mabantug ne me pangulu te nasud, wey aputanan te keet-etawan te Israil. NEW Mekeyid-u-hid-u seeye se mig-ugpe diye te Siyun ne me matubung, wey seeye se mig-ugpe ne ware igkabantali diye te bubungan te Samariya. Sikaniyu ka in-ila ne me mabantug ne me etew wey aputanan te me mahinged te Israil, ka inged ne labew te langun ne me inged. <verse number="2" style="v" />Hendiye kew wey pitawa niyu ka lungsud te Kalni, wey leus kew diye te mabantug ne lungsud te Hamat, wey tupang kew diye te lungsud te Gat ne sakup te Pilistiya. Me-meupiya naan pad seini ne me inged te Huda wey Israil? Malmaluag naa ka tane dan te tane niyu? <verse number="3" style="v" />Eggubabe kew ne egginguma ka aldew ne egsahap kew, piru nasi de iya egmahaan ka pegsahap niyu tenged te mareet ne me hinimuwan<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Migpinnuu te mareet ne hinimuwan.</char></note> niyu. <verse number="4" style="v" />Amana ne makaalat-halat ka egkeyitabu kaniyu te migmangibat-hibat de te me mahal<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Hibatanan ne migpuun te pannayew te Ilipanti.</char></note> wey te mewumel-humel ne hibatanan, wey mighibhibulung te ngalap te inalam ne nati te karniru wey te nati te baka. <verse number="5" style="v" />Nangulahing kew pad te ware karuan ne me ulahingen ne igbales niyu te alpa. Iling ki Dabid, nangimu kew degma te me alpa. <verse number="6" style="v" />Nangiinum kew te binu diye te me ubab,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: me yahung.</char></note> wey migpamaluhu te me mahal ne peemut, piru ware kew nalaggew te karereetan te Israil. <verse number="7" style="v" />Sikan naa, sikaniyu ka hun-a ne egpandakepen eyew eg-uripenen, wey egkataman e ka me kalibulungan wey me sahakeen niyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne mapahetpet ne migsaad ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Manama. Migkahi sikandin, “Igkalanlangeti ku ka pegkaambuhen te keet-etawan te Israil, wey indew-ey ku ka malig-en, matikang, wey makepal ne alad dan. Purisu igbehey ku te me kuntere ka siyudad dan duma te langun ne nakatahu kayi.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />Ne emun ke due sapulu (10) ne etew ne egkasame te sabeka ne baley, egkaamin iya man-e sikandan egpatey. <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne emun ke egginguma ka karumaan te nammatey eyew igpalihawang ka minatey diye te baley eyew egtutungen, eg-inse sikandin te minsan hentew ne diye te ledled te baley, “Duen pad lein ne duma nu rue?” Ke egtabak ka etew, “Ware!” ne egkahi e sikandin,</para>
  <para style="p">“Peeneng-eneng kad! Eg-ayad-ayad ki ne kene ta egkarawit ka ngaran te Magbebaye ne Manama.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Egtabak sikandin, “Peeneng-eneng ka! Kene ka egdawit te ngaran te Magbebaye ne Manama.”</char></note> <verse number="11" style="v" />Pammineg kew, emun ke iyan e egsuhu ka Magbebaye ne Manama, egkallundus wey egkallupet egkatamtamani ka derakel wey dereisek ne me baley. NEW Ne kuntee, pammineg kew, egsuhu ka Magbebaye ne Manama, wey igpahuhus din ka derakel wey dereisek ne me baley. <verse number="12" style="v" />Egpallahuy naa ka me kudde diye te batuwen? Igpakararu naa te etew ka me baka diye te dahat? Kene! Piru sikaniyu mule innimu niyu ne mareet ka maheteng,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Inggimu ne eggilu ka matareng ne peggukum.</char></note> wey immareet niyu ka eleg.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Ka meupiya ne behas te keupiya diye te uled te kayu.</char></note></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Migpeggasal kew te natalu niyu ka lungsud te Ludibar wey Karnaim. Ne migkahi kew, “Mannekal ki wey nareeg ta ka lungsud te Karnaim.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Piru migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Amana ne Maresen ne Manama, “Egpalusuran ku sikaniyu te sabeka ne nasud, E keet-etawan te Israil. Egbaybayaran kew nikandan puun te dalan te Hamat<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Egkakita diye te igkahibang ne balabahan dapit te igsile.</char></note> peendiye te Beuhan te Araba.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Egkakita diye te igkakawanan ne balabahan dapit te igsile.</char></note></para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka impakita ne me talangas</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Seini ka impakita keddi te Magbebaye ne Manama: Pegpitew ku, iyan kud iya se masulug ne talangas ne innimu te Magbebaye ne Manama eyew igpeuyan din te tane. Sikan pad iya napenga ka peggalab te pinamula ne baad te Hari wey ka inggalaban migbunsud e man-e ka egtubu. <verse number="2" style="v" />Ne impangeen te me talangas ka langun ne me pinamula, wey warad iya nasame. Ne migkahi a, “Magbebaye ne Manama, pasayluwa nu ka keet-etawan <note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Hakub.</char></note>nu. Egmemenu naan e sikandan eyew egkeuyag ke igpasalerep nu sika ne legpad? Mahuye wey deisek de sikandan.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Ne nabalbalawan ka suman-suman te Magbebaye ne Manama wey migkahi sikandin, “Kene egpakabulus ka nakita nu.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka impakita ne hapuy</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne duen e man-e impakita keddi te Magbebaye ne Manama. Nakita ku sikandin ne migpangandam eyew te peglegpad te langun pinaahi te hapuy. Neetiyan ka weyig diye te diralem te tane tenged te hapuy, wey nasilaban e ka katantanaan. <verse number="5" style="v" />Ne migkahi a, “E Magbebaye ne Manama, ipeeneng-eneng nud ubag sika se meinit! Egmemenu naan e sikandan eyew egkeuyag ke igpasalerep nu sika ne legpad? Mahuye wey deisek de sikandan.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Ne nabalbalawan ka suman-suman te Magbebaye ne Manama wey migkahi sikandin, “Kene ded iya man-e egpakapabulus ka nakita nu.”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka impakita ne Tuntun</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Ne duen e man-e impakita keddi te Magbebaye ne Manama. Nakita ku ka Magbebaye ne Manama ne migsasindeg lenged te matikang wey makepal ne alad ne miggehen-gen te tuntun ne igseked. <verse number="8" style="v" />Ne mig-insaan a te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Nekey-a ka nakita nu, Amus?” Ne migtabak a, “Tuntun ne igseked.” Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Eggamiten ku seini ne tuntun eyew igpapitew ku ka seyyup te me matig-Israil. Ne kene ne matul-id iling te matul-id ne alad ne matikang wey makepal. Ne kenad e egkabalbalawan ka suman-suman ku te pegdusa kandan. <verse number="9" style="v" />Eglundusen ku ka me panubaran ne diye te matikang ne inged ne insimbaan te me matig-Israil, wey egpalusuran ku te me kuntere ka me kabuhalan ni Hari Hirubuwam.” NEW Egkengalundus ka me panubaran te me kabuhalan ni Isaak, wey egkengaguhus ka me matulus ne simbaanan te Israil. Egguleen ku te egpangimatey ka me kabuhalan ni Hirubuwam.”</para>
  <para style="s">Si Amus wey si Amasiyas</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" />Ne migpanaha te lalag si Amasiyas ne ahalen ne pari te Bitil, diye ki Hirubuwam ne Hari te Israil, ne miggenendue, “Intipu ni Amus ka me etew eyew eggimatayan ka. Egpakarereet te nasud ka me lalag din. <verse number="11" style="v" />Su kahi rin, ‘Eggimatayan si Hirubuwam te kuntere din, wey egpandakepen e ka keet-etawan te Israil wey eg-uripenen e diye te mariyu te inged dan.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" />Ne migkahiyan ni Amasiyas si Amus, “Eleg e, prupita! Libed kad diye te Huda wey diye ka panagne eyew egpakeenen ka nikandan. <verse number="13" style="v" />Kene kad panagne kayi te Bitil su kayi ka timplu wey ka palasyu te Hari.” <verse number="14" style="v" />Ne migtabak si Amus ki Amasiyas, “Kena-a ne prupita wey ke anak naa te prupita. Talagtameng a mule te karniru wey talagtanggu degma te me kayu ne sikumuru. <verse number="15" style="v" />Piru impaawa a te Magbebaye ne Manama puun te pegtameng te me karniru wey ingkahiyan a, ‘Hipanew ka wey panagne ka diye te keet-etawan ku te Israil.’ <verse number="16" style="v" />Purisu pammineha nu ka lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama. Imbalabahan a nikeykew ka egpanagne diye te keet-etawan te Israil wey ka egwali diye te me kabuhalan ni Isaak. <verse number="17" style="v" />Tenged due, seini ka ingkahi te Magbebaye ne Manama keykew, ‘Ka asawa nu egkeyimu ne egpabaley-baley ne malitan te siyudad, wey ka me anak nu egkabbunu. Egsekeren wey egba-baaren te duma ne me etew ka tane nu, wey diye ka egpatey te inged ne ware egpalintutuu te Manama. Ne ka keet-etawan te Israil, egpanguripenen diye te inged ne mariyu te ugpaan dan.’ ”</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka impakita ne bukag ne napenu te prutas</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ne duen e man-e impakita keddi te Magbebaye ne Manama. Iyan ku nakita se bukag ne napenu te me prutas. <verse number="2" style="v" />Ne mig-insaan a te Magbebaye ne Manama, “Nekey-a ka nakita nu Amus?”</para>
  <para style="p">Ne migtabak a, “Iyan ku nakita se sabeka ne bukag ne napenu te me prutas.”</para>
  <para style="p">Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Iling te seini se me behas te kayu ne neneyinuhan, ka keet-etawan te Israil eleg e ne eglegparan! Ne kenad e egkabalbalawan ka suman-suman ku te peglegpad kandan. <verse number="3" style="v" />Te sika ne aldew, ka me ulahingen diye te palasyu, egkeyimu e ne me ulahingen te peglungku. Egpekeempet ka me minatey te minsan hendei. Egpangenaten ka me minatey peendiye te lihawangan te siyudad te ware lalahan,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="s">Eglegparan te Manama ka Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" />Pammineg kew, sikaniyu se migleig-leig te egkengaayu-ayu wey migpakannekal ne egdereet te ware egkengeyimu. <verse number="5" style="v" />Migkahi kew, “Kene key e egpakatahad ne egkeepus ka Aldew te Peggimeley eyew egpakapamelegye key e te me trigu ney. Ken-u naan pad egkeepus ka aldew te peggimeley, eyew egpakapamelegye key e man-e? Igbelegye ney te mahal seini, eggamiten ney ka kene ne eleg ne takesanan wey egbalbalawan ney ka timbangan eyew egkalimbungan ka egpameli. <verse number="6" style="v" />Igbelegye ney te mahal ka insamsamilian ne trigu, wey egbeliyen ney ka egkaayu-ayu ne kene egpakabayad te utang din eyew eg-uripenen. Ne egsaliyuwan ney man-e te senge sukub ne sandal ka ware egkeyimu ne kene egpakabayad te utang din.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Ne migpahunlibet ka Magbebaye ne Manama, ka Manama te Israil ne migkahi, “Kene kud iya eglingawan ka mareet ne hinimuwan dan. <verse number="8" style="v" />Sikan naa, egpalinuhan ku ka tane wey egkalaggew ka langun ne nangugpe te inged. Egkeenat wey egpakalenep de man-e ka tane iling te weyig te Nilu diye te Ihiptu. <verse number="9" style="v" />“Te sika ne aldew, egpalineben ku ka aldew minsan meudtu pad wey egpaddusilem ka aldew, kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama. <verse number="10" style="v" />Eggimuwen ku ne timpu te peglungku ka timpu te me pegsahakeen niyu wey ka me ulahingen niyu te peggale-gale egkeyimu ne me ulahingen peglungku. Egpasaluuben ku sikaniyu te saku wey egpaabuluhan ku sikaniyu. Ne egpekeiling kew te me amey wey me iney ne miglungku te namatey ne sabsabbeka ne anak dan. Amana iya ne masumpit ka egtamanan te seeye ne aldew.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Egginguma ka timpu ne egpeyingumaan ku te bitil ka inged. Egmanggutasan ka keet-etawan, piru kene te egkakeen, wey egkammaraan sikandan, piru kene te weyig. Egmanggutasan sikandan te lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama. <verse number="12" style="v" />Egleleuhen dan ka karagdahatan wey katantanaan puun te igsile peendiye te iglineb, eyew egpammitew te lalag te Magbebaye ne Manama, piru kene dan egkatulituan. <verse number="13" style="v" />Egkammaraan te sika ne aldew ka me kanakan wey ka mateles ne me mengebay, wey egkengalepu sikandan. <verse number="14" style="v" />Egdereetan seeye se migsaad te ngaran te me diyus-diyus te Samariya wey migkahi “Mengeyibet te ngaran te diyus-diyus te Dan,” wey “Mengeyibet te ngaran te diyus-diyus te Birsiba,” wey kenad sikandan egpakasasindeg pad man-e.</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" />
  <para style="s">Ka peggukum te Magbebaye ne Manama</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" />Ne nakita ku ne migsasindeg ka Magbebaye ne Manama diye te kakiliran te altar, wey migkahi, “Panlampesi nu ka sungkaleg te timplu, eyew egkawelwel ka me pabunsuran. Panlupeta nu eyew egkengeuluhan ka me ulu te me etew. Ne ka egkasame, igpabunu kud, wey warad iya egpakapallahuy kandan wey egkaamin dan egpatey. <verse number="2" style="v" />Minsan eglulungag pad sikandan diye te inged te me minatey<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: Siyul.</char></note>, egkeumaan ded sikandan te belad ku puun diye. Minsan egpamaneyik pad sikandan diye te langit, igpepamaneug ku red sikandan puun diye. <verse number="3" style="v" />Minsan eggeles sikandan diye te ampew te bubungan te Karmil, egpamitawen ku wey egpandakepen ku sikandan puun diye. Minsan eggeles sikandan diye te diralem te dahat, egsuhuen ku ka bubuyahen ne uled diye eyew egdawiyen sikandan. <verse number="4" style="v" />Ne emun egkarakep sikandan te me kuntere dan, egpeyimatayan ku sikandan pinaahi te kampilan. Egpakasalerep sikandan te karereetan, kene ne keupinan.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" />Ne insamsam te Magbebaye ne Manama ne Amana ne Maresen ne Manama ka tane,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey naleney seini,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey miglungku ka langun ne nangugpe kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpakalepew ka tane wey egpakalenep de man-e iling te weyig ne Nilu diye te Ihiptu.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" />Miggimu sikandin te sinabeng diye te langit,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey diye din ipabunsud te tane ka pabunsuran kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">Inlimud din ka me weyig diye te aw-awangan puun te dahat</para>
  <para style="q2">wey impalugsu din seini isip uran diye te tane.</para>
  <para style="q1">Iyan din ngaran ka Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" />Ne migkahi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, “Keet-etawan te Israil, nekeg-iling de ka pegtengteng ku kaniyu te matig-Itiyupiya. Impalihawang ku sikaniyu puun te Ihiptu wey ka me matig-Pilistihanun puun te Kaptur, wey ka matig-Aram puun te Kir. <verse number="8" style="v" />Sikeddi ka Magbebaye ne Manama, egtanudtanud te me matig-Israil<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Te Hibruwanen: migharian</char></note> ne makasesale wey egguleen ku seini kayi te ampew te tane. Piru kene ku eg-aminen te eggimatey ka kabuhalan ni Hakub,” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" />“Egsuhu a ne egpasiliyen ka me matig-Israil wey ka me mahinged te duma ne me inged iling te pegpasili te triggu piru ware minsan sabeka ne lehas ne egkeulug diye te tane. <verse number="10" style="v" />Egkengamatey ka langun ne keet-etawan ku te pegpabunbunuey, seeye se egkahi te ‘Kene ki iya egsahap wey ware mareet ne egginguma kanta.’ ”</para>
  <para style="s">Ka egginguma ne pegpalibed te pegpasasindeg te Israil</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" />
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:11-12: </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">Him 15:16-18.</char>
    </note> “Te seeye ne aldew, igpasasindeg ku eg-abeyi ka ugpaan ni Dabid ne nahuhus wey eg-ay-ayaran ku ka me alad kayi ne nahuhus. Igpasasindeg ku red man-e seini ne iling te dengan ne timpu. <verse number="12" style="v" />Sikan naa, egkaangken dan ka tane ne nasame te Idum wey ka langun ne nasud ne keddi dengan, ” kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama ne iyan eggimu kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Ne migkahi pad man-e ka Magbebaye ne Manama,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Te seeye ne aldew taheed te eggaani pad ka duma, egdaru e ka duma,</para>
  <para style="q2">egkekeles pad te ubas ka duma, ne egsawed e te beni ka duma.</para>
  <para style="q1">Egpanihis ka meemis ne binu puun te me bubungan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egpanulayas man-e puun te me tuhal.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />Igmalibed ku ka neneuripen ne keet-etawan ku,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey egbalbalawan dan te eggimu ka nahuhus ne me siyudad dan,</para>
  <para style="q2">wey diyad e sikandan egmangugpe.</para>
  <para style="q2">Egmammula sikandan te paras wey egmanginum te binu te ubas,</para>
  <para style="q2">egmammula wey egmangeen sikandan te me behas kayi.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" />Igpeugpe ku ka matig-Israil diye te tane dan mismu.</para>
  <para style="q2">Ne kenad sikandan egkarelrel puun te tane ne imbehey ku kandan,”</para>
  <para style="q2">kahi te Magbebaye ne Manama, ne Manama niyu.</para>
</usx>